<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">بَابُ:</span> الِانْتِبَاذِ فِي الْأَوْعِيَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٣٤٥ - قَدْ صَحَّ عَنْ رَسُولِ اللَّهِ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ أَنَّهُ <span class="c2">«نَهَى عَنِ الدُّبَّاءِ، وَالْمِزَفِّتِ»</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَاخْتَلَفَ الْعُلَمَاءُ هَلْ ذَلِكَ النَّهْيُ بَاقٍ أَمْ نُسِخَ؟ .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">فَقَالَ بَعْضُهُمْ:</span> هُوَ نَهْيُ كَرَاهَةٍ، وَحُكْمُهُ بَاقٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَهَذَا مَرْوِيٌّ عَنْ مَالِكٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ آخَرُونَ:</span> نُسِخَ بِحَدِيثِ بُرَيْدَةَ،<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>